**How it works:**
- Player checks "Play chord progressions" on start screen, picks a tier, and starts
- Instead of random chords, the game cycles through real progressions (e.g., "Pop Classic": C → G → Am → F)
- After completing a progression, a new random one is picked for the same tier
- The progression name and position indicator show below the chord notes
- When unchecked, behavior is unchanged (random chords)